N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1211.110 - Poisonous gas or liquid, Class A
State Regulations

No vehicle shall enter either a tunnel, the George

Washington Bridge Lower Level or George Washington Bridge Expressway if its
load includes any poisonous gas or liquid, Class A except there shall be no
restrictions on the transportation of gas identification sets, loaded or empty. Empty containers which last contained a poisonous gas or liquid, Class A, are
not allowed passage. Notes
